MARK YOUR CALENDAR - Back by popular demand!


Ziff Energy Group presents the


2002 Gas Storage Conference

February 6-7 in Houston


This popular Gas Storage Conference has been expanded to a two-day event and includes an exciting agenda that will not be found at any other conference.  Featuring:


Storage supply/demand update


New storage projects


New storage pricing scenarios


New storage technology


The latest about Compressed Air Energy Storage (CAES) facilities


Special workshops


Storage Project displays


Watch for the detailed agenda to be released in November, and frequently visit www.ziffenergyconferences.com for updated information.


